          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Detroit</placeName>
                                        <date>May 25<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed please<lb/> find draft for $27.75 on
                                                  <placeName>N. Y.</placeName> for those<lb/> 10
                                        volumes of the <sic>occident</sic>.</p>
                              <p>I could not procure a draft on <placeName>Phild.</placeName><lb/>
                                        or should have taken one for that place<lb/> however most
                                        any merchant of your city<lb/> will cash it for you at
                                        par.</p>
                              <p>Those ten volumes of the occident were recd.<lb/> in good order
                                        &amp; neatly bound also 2 prayer<lb/> and 2 spelling books
                                        which we shall endeavor<lb/> to introduce to some of our
                                        friends &amp;<lb/> make you returns as soon as disposed
                                        of.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mr Brissler</persName> is not in town
                                        just now<lb/> shall present him your bill on his return<lb/>
                                        I should be very glad to <sic>wellcome</sic> you<lb/> in
                                                  <placeName>Detroit</placeName> during the ensuing
                                                  <sic>sumer</sic></p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Please acknowledge recpt.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <persName role="author">Joseph Freidman</persName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
